title: 47. Wildfires, Cops, and Keggers
description: On Election Day, most people focus on the obvious winners and losers -- that is, the candidates. But we went looking for some of the strange side effects that elections produce.
author: editor@freakonomics.com (Freakonomics Radio + Stitcher)
